# NAME

schoolmesh\_loginaccount\_changeshell - Change the shell for the login account of a user

# SYNOPSIS

schoolmesh\_loginaccount\_changeshell *username* *shell*

# DESCRIPTION

Use this script to change the shell of a user. The shell must be one of those
defined in /etc/shells.

# EXAMPLES

	schoolmesh_loginaccount_changeshell john /bin/bash

